## Client-side environment variables (Vite)
#
# Local development:
# - Vite proxy will forward `/api` to `VITE_API_URL`
# - Vite proxy will forward `/reco-api` to `VITE_RECO_API_URL`
#
# Production:
# - Prefer using a reverse proxy / same-origin deployment (so you may not need these)

VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
VITE_RECO_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
VITE_CHAT_API_URL=/reco-api/api/chat

